	bool "USB Support"
	depends on MV88F5181 || MV88F5180N || MV88F5182 || MV88F5082 || MV88F5181L || MV88F6082 || MV88F6183 || MV88F6281 || MV78XX0
	default y
        ---help---
        Please don't change this configs unless you know what you are doing.

